<li><a href="/wiki/Uki_Go%C3%B1i" title="Uki Goñi">Goñi, Uki</a>. <i>The Real Odessa: Smuggling the Nazis to Perón's Argentina</i>. London: Granta (revised), 2003.</li>
<li>Graham, Robert; Alvarez, David (1998). <i>Nothing Sacred: Nazi Espionage against the Vatican, 1939-1945</i>. London: Frank Cass, 1998.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Gitta_Sereny" title="Gitta Sereny">Sereny, Gitta</a> (1977). <i>Into That Darkness</i>. London: <a href="/wiki/Picador_(imprint)" title="Picador (imprint)">Picador</a>, 1977.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Gerald_Steinacher" title="Gerald Steinacher">Steinacher, Gerald</a>. <i>The Cape of Last Hope: The Flight of Nazi War Criminals through Italy to South America</i>, in Eisterer, Klaus; Bischof, Günter (ed.) (2006). <i>Transatlantic Relations: Austria and Latin America in the 19th and 20th Century</i> (Transatlantica 1), 203 – 224. New Brunswick: Transatlantica, 2006.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Simon_Wiesenthal" title="Simon Wiesenthal">Wiesenthal, Simon</a> (1989). <i>Justice not Vengeance</i>. London: <a href="/wiki/Weidenfeld_%26_Nicolson" title="Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson">Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson</a>, 1989.</li>
</ul>


